@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kofxli(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = v0
    v2 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.94 - v2 + 0.86) - (v1 + 0.34 * v0 + 0.30)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.75 / v2 + 0.11) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.57)))
    data[tid] = v0
